[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A BrowserProvider is intended to wrap an injected provider which adheres to the EIP-1193 standard, which most (if not all) currently do.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] Connect to the ethereum provider, optionally forcing the network.
