[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A MinedTransactionResponse is an interface representing a transaction which has been mined and allows for a type guard for its property values being defined.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The block hash this transaction occurred in.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The block number this transaction occurred in.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A NetworkPlugin provides additional functionality on a Network.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] It is recommended to use reverse-domain-notation, which permits unique names with a known authority as well as hierarchal entries.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A NonceManager wraps another Signer and automatically manages the nonce, ensuring serialized and sequential nonces are used during transaction.
