[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] This cannot change state and has no cost in ether, as it is effectively simulating execution.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] This can be used to have the Blockchain perform computations based on its state (e.g. running a Contract's getters) or to simulate the effect of a transaction before actually performing an operation.
