[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A TransactionReceipt includes additional information about a transaction that is only available after it has been mined.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The block hash of the Block this transaction was included in.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The block number of the Block this transaction was included in.
