[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] A TransactionResponse includes all properties about a transaction that was sent to the network, which may or may not be included in a block.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The transactionResponse.isMined can be used to check if the transaction has been mined as well as type guard that the otherwise possibly null properties are defined.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The EIP-2930 access list for transaction types that support it, otherwise null.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p01] The blockHash of the block that this transaction was included in.
