[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p02] If null, then the transaction is an initcode transaction.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p02] This means the result of executing the data will be deployed as a new contract on chain (assuming it does not revert) and the address may be computed using getCreateAddress.
[src:ethers-js/api-providers-p02] This is 0 for legacy transactions types.
